{"tid":1913881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃毓民宣布不參選 籲支持者不要投票","createTime":"2020-03-07T06:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T13:15:30.000Z","uid":297241,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ceb54eaf7e368f07a447e019dff78b43cc0bdb","tid":1913881,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:54:32.000Z","msg":"黃毓民宣布不參選 <br />\n籲支持者不要投票<br />\n<br />\n立法會九龍西補選在11月25日舉行，前立法會議員黃<span style=\"color: red;\">毓民晚上宣布不會參選及呼籲支持者不要投票</span>。他強調，自己早已表明不會參選，「重大宣告就係三不一沒有」，即不參選、不助選、不投票。他指出劉小麗及游蕙禎是遭當局無理DQ，因為政治倫理，所以決不會參加不義的選舉。他又解釋「沒有」，即<span style=\"color: red;\">民主派立法會議員沒有不總辭的理由，認為應焦土抗戰，如果不總辭即是等如賣港</span>。"},{"pid":"38fae7cd83fef1b188cefa6d442d1a243b41454a","tid":1913881,"uid":201464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:56:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2018</span></span><br />\n又要開幾多個post？"},{"pid":"fb0adc7e584c3e423b22d7d7f179cc30e78df645","tid":1913881,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"又叫人射落海。"},{"pid":"626d0364861b42cbbc970b3e7e116412f37dbc79","tid":1913881,"uid":99827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"補選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e5c8e2ce620f7b3db7bd995233c7a4e3ddb773","tid":1913881,"uid":2569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T07:00:49.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<br />\nBlock樓主 and 拉"},{"pid":"00c1ab43e34a9701647e9f5a8e4756d1fbb1893e","tid":1913881,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T07:01:08.000Z","msg":"總辭有乜柒用 即係小朋友發爛渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a930833d7dcc2fdaab4eab3d6c49129cd4024d","tid":1913881,"uid":54223,"like":2,"di